{"type": "article", "id": 28329, "title": "两用浇水壶", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-17T06:40:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152431xWtpmVUKePN3l80O.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>浇水壶也可以既实用又有高颜值，<a href=\"http://www.aristotelisbarakos.com/\">Aristotelis Barakos</a> 最近就设计了一款可以两用的浇水壶 Two Way。正如它名字所指的那样，你可以通过两个出水口以不同的方式为花草浇水。如果浇完之后还有剩余的水，你还可以把它当作花器使用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152428JZAyhSwFXlx7CpPa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152428LO5eTEIaDZlnVJ1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152429CDoX2Yl9S7LecIv6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152431YCzjsc8eQFkdNGPS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}